## Creating a Module

Create a file `math.js`:
```javascript
// math.js
const add = (a, b) => a + b;
const subtract = (a, b) => a - b;

module.exports = { add, subtract };
```

`module.exports` is an object that will be returned when another file `require`s this file. You can export anything â€“ functions, objects, primitives.

